









Archboot options and troubleshooting:
- If your system hangs during the boot process, any combinations of the
  boot options: 'noapic acpi=off pci=routeirq nosmp nomsi' may be useful.
- Some hardware doesn't like the KMS activation, use nouveau.modeset=0
  or radeon.modeset=0 or i915.modeset=0 or nomodeset on boot prompt.

